headline: Margherita Maccapani Missoni Releases Personal Collection of Vintage and Pre-Loved Fashion on eBay
summary: eBay announces the latest in its series of exclusive drops from the closets of fashion and entertainment's most influential figures with 'From The Collection: Margherita Maccapani Missoni.' The collection features exclusive pre-owned, vintage and archival pieces curated by the fashion tastemaker, available for auction now through December 12 at ebay.com/margherita-maccapani-missoni.
